# Clean Code

- Small functions and classes with a single responsibility
- Prefer clear names over comments; comment only non-obvious intent
- Avoid deep nesting; early-return instead
- No unused imports, dead code, or speculative abstractions
- Match existing naming and file layout before inventing new patterns
- Keep PRs/changes focused — do not refactor unrelated code
